msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_WhiteDragon_Desc"
msgid ""
"Medda, a resident of Hateno Village, told you\n"
"that there is a <1.se_co>Spring of Wisdom<2.re_co> somewhere on\n"
"Mount Lanayru, which towers to the north\n"
"of the village. The story goes that long ago,\n"
"a princess used that spring for a purification\n"
"ceremony. \n"
"\n"
"Moreover, there are rumors of a fantastic\n"
"treasure hidden in the <3.se_co>spring<4.re_co>."
msgstr ""

