msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_WhiteDragon_Finish"
msgid ""
"When you tossed <1.se_co>Naydra's scale<2.re_co> into the\n"
"Spring of Wisdom, an ancient shrine appeared.\n"
"\n"
"Freed of the shackles of evil, Naydra flew\n"
"away in peace."
msgstr ""

