msgid ""
"You freed <1.se_co>Naydra<2.re_co>, the guardian dragon of the\n"
"Mount Lanayru spring, from the darkness that\n"
"had overcome it.\n"
"\n"
"When <3.se_co>Naydra <4.re_co>soared away into the heavens,\n"
"it left behind <5.se_co>Naydra's scale<6.re_co>."
